{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.1","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:1","prev_osis_id":"Mark.005.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9sus \u00e0 Nazareth. Incr\u00e9dulit\u00e9 des habitants<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. (Mt 13:54-58.) Lu 4:16-30. Ro 10:21.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    J\u00e9sus partit de l\u00e0, et se rendit dans sa patrie. Ses disciples le suivirent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.2","name":"Marc 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.5.43","name":"Marc 5:43","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.5.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.2","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:2","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Quand le sabbat fut venu, il se mit \u00e0 enseigner dans la synagogue. Beaucoup de gens qui l\u2019entendirent \u00e9taient \u00e9tonn\u00e9s et disaient: D\u2019o\u00f9 lui viennent ces choses? Quelle est cette sagesse qui lui a \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9e, et comment de tels miracles se font-ils par ses mains?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.3","name":"Marc 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.1","name":"Marc 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.3","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:3","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>N\u2019est-ce pas le charpentier, le fils de Marie, le fr\u00e8re de Jacques, de Joses, de Jude et de Simon? Et ses s\u0153urs ne sont-elles pas ici parmi nous? Et il \u00e9tait pour eux une occasion de chute.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.4","name":"Marc 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.2","name":"Marc 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.4","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:4","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Mais J\u00e9sus leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Un proph\u00e8te n\u2019est m\u00e9pris\u00e9 que dans sa patrie, parmi ses parents, et dans sa maison.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.5","name":"Marc 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.3","name":"Marc 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.5","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:5","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il ne put faire l\u00e0 aucun miracle, si ce n\u2019est qu\u2019il imposa les mains \u00e0 quelques malades et les gu\u00e9rit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.6","name":"Marc 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.4","name":"Marc 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.6","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:6","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Et il s\u2019\u00e9tonnait de leur incr\u00e9dulit\u00e9.<\/p>\n<h3 class=\"s\">Mission des douze ap\u00f4tres<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-13: cf. (Mt 10; 11:1. Lu 9:1-6.) Lu 10:1-20.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\">\n    J\u00e9sus parcourait les villages d\u2019alentour, en enseignant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.7","name":"Marc 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.5","name":"Marc 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.7","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:7","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Alors il appela les douze, et il commen\u00e7a \u00e0 les envoyer deux \u00e0 deux, en leur donnant pouvoir sur les esprits impurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.8","name":"Marc 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.6","name":"Marc 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.8","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:8","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il leur prescrivit de ne rien prendre pour le voyage, si ce n\u2019est un b\u00e2ton; de n\u2019avoir ni pain, ni sac, ni monnaie dans la ceinture;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.9","name":"Marc 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.7","name":"Marc 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.9","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:9","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>de chausser des sandales, et de ne pas rev\u00eatir deux tuniques.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.10","name":"Marc 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.8","name":"Marc 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.10","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:10","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Puis il leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Dans quelque maison que vous entriez, restez-y jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que vous partiez de ce lieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.11","name":"Marc 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.9","name":"Marc 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.11","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:11","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et, s\u2019il y a quelque part des gens qui ne vous re\u00e7oivent ni ne vous \u00e9coutent, retirez-vous de l\u00e0, et<\/span><span class=\"wj\">secouez la poussi\u00e8re de vos pieds, afin que cela leur serve de t\u00e9moignage.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.12","name":"Marc 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.10","name":"Marc 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.12","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:12","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ils partirent, et ils pr\u00each\u00e8rent la repentance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.13","name":"Marc 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.11","name":"Marc 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.13","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:13","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ils chassaient beaucoup de d\u00e9mons, et ils oignaient d\u2019huile beaucoup de malades et les gu\u00e9rissaient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.14","name":"Marc 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.12","name":"Marc 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.14","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:14","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.015,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Mort de Jean-Baptiste<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 14-29: cf. (Mt 14:1-12.) Lu 9:7-9; 3:19, 20.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>\n    Le roi H\u00e9rode entendit parler de J\u00e9sus, dont le nom \u00e9tait devenu c\u00e9l\u00e8bre, et il dit: Jean-Baptiste est ressuscit\u00e9 des morts, et c\u2019est pour cela qu\u2019il se fait par lui des miracles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.15","name":"Marc 6:15","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.13","name":"Marc 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.15","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:15","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>D\u2019autres disaient: C\u2019est \u00c9lie. Et d\u2019autres disaient: C\u2019est un proph\u00e8te comme l\u2019un des proph\u00e8tes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.16","name":"Marc 6:16","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.14","name":"Marc 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.16","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:16","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Mais H\u00e9rode, en apprenant cela, disait: Ce Jean que j\u2019ai fait d\u00e9capiter, c\u2019est lui qui est ressuscit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.17","name":"Marc 6:17","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.15","name":"Marc 6:15","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.17","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:17","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Car H\u00e9rode lui-m\u00eame avait fait arr\u00eater Jean, et l\u2019avait fait lier en prison, \u00e0 cause d\u2019H\u00e9rodias, femme de Philippe, son fr\u00e8re, parce qu\u2019il l\u2019avait \u00e9pous\u00e9e,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.18","name":"Marc 6:18","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.16","name":"Marc 6:16","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.18","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:18","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>et que Jean lui disait: Il ne t\u2019est pas permis d\u2019avoir la femme de ton fr\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.19","name":"Marc 6:19","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.17","name":"Marc 6:17","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.19","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:19","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>H\u00e9rodias \u00e9tait irrit\u00e9e contre Jean, et voulait le faire mourir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.20","name":"Marc 6:20","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.18","name":"Marc 6:18","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.20","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:20","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Mais elle ne le pouvait; car H\u00e9rode craignait Jean, le connaissant pour un homme juste et saint; il le prot\u00e9geait, et, apr\u00e8s l\u2019avoir entendu, il \u00e9tait souvent perplexe, et l\u2019\u00e9coutait avec plaisir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.21","name":"Marc 6:21","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.19","name":"Marc 6:19","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.21","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:21","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Cependant, un jour propice arriva, lorsque H\u00e9rode, \u00e0 l\u2019anniversaire de sa naissance, donna un festin \u00e0 ses grands, aux chefs militaires et aux principaux de la Galil\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.22","name":"Marc 6:22","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.20","name":"Marc 6:20","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.22","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:22","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>La fille d\u2019H\u00e9rodias entra dans la salle; elle dansa, et plut \u00e0 H\u00e9rode et \u00e0 ses convives. Le roi dit \u00e0 la jeune fille: Demande-moi ce que tu voudras, et je te le donnerai.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.23","name":"Marc 6:23","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.21","name":"Marc 6:21","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.23","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:23","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Il ajouta avec serment: Ce que tu me demanderas, je te le donnerai, f\u00fbt-ce la moiti\u00e9 de mon royaume.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.24","name":"Marc 6:24","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.22","name":"Marc 6:22","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.24","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:24","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>\u00c9tant sortie, elle dit \u00e0 sa m\u00e8re: Que demanderai-je? Et sa m\u00e8re r\u00e9pondit: La t\u00eate de Jean-Baptiste.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.25","name":"Marc 6:25","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.23","name":"Marc 6:23","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.25","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:25","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Elle s\u2019empressa de rentrer aussit\u00f4t vers le roi, et lui fit cette demande: Je veux que tu me donnes \u00e0 l\u2019instant, sur un plat, la t\u00eate de Jean-Baptiste.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.26","name":"Marc 6:26","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.24","name":"Marc 6:24","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.26","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:26","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Le roi fut attrist\u00e9; mais, \u00e0 cause de ses serments et des convives, il ne voulut pas lui faire un refus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.27","name":"Marc 6:27","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.25","name":"Marc 6:25","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.27","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:27","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Il envoya sur-le-champ un garde, avec ordre d\u2019apporter la t\u00eate de Jean-Baptiste.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.28","name":"Marc 6:28","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.26","name":"Marc 6:26","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.28","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:28","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Le garde alla d\u00e9capiter Jean dans la prison, et apporta la t\u00eate sur un plat. Il la donna \u00e0 la jeune fille, et la jeune fille la donna \u00e0 sa m\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.29","name":"Marc 6:29","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.27","name":"Marc 6:27","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.29","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:29","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Les disciples de Jean, ayant appris cela, vinrent prendre son corps, et le mirent dans un s\u00e9pulcre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.30","name":"Marc 6:30","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.28","name":"Marc 6:28","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.30","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:30","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.031,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Multiplication des pains<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 30-44: cf. (Mt 14:13-21. Lu 9:10-17. Jn 6:1-14.) Mc 8:1-9.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>\n    Les ap\u00f4tres, s\u2019\u00e9tant rassembl\u00e9s aupr\u00e8s de J\u00e9sus, lui racont\u00e8rent tout ce qu\u2019ils avaient fait et tout ce qu\u2019ils avaient enseign\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.31","name":"Marc 6:31","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.29","name":"Marc 6:29","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.31","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:31","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>J\u00e9sus leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Venez \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9cart dans un lieu d\u00e9sert, et reposez-vous un peu.<\/span> Car il y avait beaucoup d\u2019allants et de venants, et ils n\u2019avaient m\u00eame pas le temps de manger.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.32","name":"Marc 6:32","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.30","name":"Marc 6:30","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.32","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:32","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Ils partirent donc dans une barque, pour aller \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9cart dans un lieu d\u00e9sert.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.33","name":"Marc 6:33","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.31","name":"Marc 6:31","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.33","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:33","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Beaucoup de gens les virent s\u2019en aller et les reconnurent, et de toutes les villes on accourut \u00e0 pied et on les devan\u00e7a au lieu o\u00f9 ils se rendaient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.34","name":"Marc 6:34","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.32","name":"Marc 6:32","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.34","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:34","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Quand il sortit de la barque, J\u00e9sus vit une grande foule, et fut \u00e9mu de compassion pour eux, parce qu\u2019ils \u00e9taient comme des brebis qui n\u2019ont point de berger; et il se mit \u00e0 leur enseigner beaucoup de choses.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.35","name":"Marc 6:35","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.33","name":"Marc 6:33","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.35","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:35","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Comme l\u2019heure \u00e9tait d\u00e9j\u00e0 avanc\u00e9e, ses disciples s\u2019approch\u00e8rent de lui, et dirent: Ce lieu est d\u00e9sert, et l\u2019heure est d\u00e9j\u00e0 avanc\u00e9e;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.36","name":"Marc 6:36","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.34","name":"Marc 6:34","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.36","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:36","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>renvoie-les, afin qu\u2019ils aillent dans les campagnes et dans les villages des environs, pour s\u2019acheter de quoi manger.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.37","name":"Marc 6:37","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.35","name":"Marc 6:35","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.37","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:37","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>J\u00e9sus leur r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">Donnez-leur vous-m\u00eames \u00e0 manger.<\/span> Mais ils lui dirent: Irions-nous acheter des pains pour deux cents deniers, et leur donnerions-nous \u00e0 manger?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.38","name":"Marc 6:38","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.36","name":"Marc 6:36","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.38","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:38","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Et il leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Combien avez-vous de pains? Allez voir.<\/span> Ils s\u2019en assur\u00e8rent, et r\u00e9pondirent: Cinq, et deux poissons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.39","name":"Marc 6:39","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.37","name":"Marc 6:37","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.39","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:39","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>Alors il leur commanda de les faire tous asseoir par groupes sur l\u2019herbe verte,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.40","name":"Marc 6:40","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.38","name":"Marc 6:38","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.40","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:40","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>et ils s\u2019assirent par rang\u00e9es de cent et de cinquante.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.41","name":"Marc 6:41","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.39","name":"Marc 6:39","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.41","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:41","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.042,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>Il prit les cinq pains et les deux poissons et, levant les yeux vers le ciel, il rendit gr\u00e2ces. Puis, il rompit les pains, et les donna aux disciples, afin qu\u2019ils les distribuassent \u00e0 la foule. Il partagea aussi les deux poissons entre tous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.42","name":"Marc 6:42","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.40","name":"Marc 6:40","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.42","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:42","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>Tous mang\u00e8rent et furent rassasi\u00e9s,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.43","name":"Marc 6:43","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.41","name":"Marc 6:41","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.43","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:43","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>et l\u2019on emporta douze paniers pleins de morceaux de pain et de ce qui restait des poissons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.44","name":"Marc 6:44","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.42","name":"Marc 6:42","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.44","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:44","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>Ceux qui avaient mang\u00e9 les pains \u00e9taient cinq mille hommes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.45","name":"Marc 6:45","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.43","name":"Marc 6:43","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.45","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:45","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.046,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9sus marche sur les eaux<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 45-52: cf. (Mt 14:22-33. Jn 6:15-21.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup>\n    Aussit\u00f4t apr\u00e8s, il obligea ses disciples \u00e0 monter dans la barque et \u00e0 passer avant lui de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9, vers Bethsa\u00efda, pendant que lui-m\u00eame renverrait la foule.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.46","name":"Marc 6:46","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.44","name":"Marc 6:44","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.46","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:46","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.047,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup>Quand il l\u2019eut renvoy\u00e9e, il s\u2019en alla sur la montagne, pour prier.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.47","name":"Marc 6:47","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.45","name":"Marc 6:45","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.47","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:47","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup>Le soir \u00e9tant venu, la barque \u00e9tait au milieu de la mer, et J\u00e9sus \u00e9tait seul \u00e0 terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.48","name":"Marc 6:48","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.46","name":"Marc 6:46","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.48","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:48","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup>Il vit qu\u2019ils avaient beaucoup de peine \u00e0 ramer; car le vent leur \u00e9tait contraire. A la quatri\u00e8me veille de la nuit environ, il alla vers eux, marchant sur la mer, et il voulait les d\u00e9passer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.49","name":"Marc 6:49","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.47","name":"Marc 6:47","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.49","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:49","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.050,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup>Quand ils le virent marcher sur la mer, ils crurent que c\u2019\u00e9tait un fant\u00f4me, et ils pouss\u00e8rent des cris;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.50","name":"Marc 6:50","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.50"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.48","name":"Marc 6:48","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"50","lastverse":"50","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.50","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.50","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:50","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.051,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.50\" class=\"v\">50<\/sup>car ils le voyaient tous, et ils \u00e9taient troubl\u00e9s. Aussit\u00f4t J\u00e9sus leur parla, et leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Rassurez-vous, c\u2019est moi, n\u2019ayez pas peur!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.51","name":"Marc 6:51","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.51"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.49","name":"Marc 6:49","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"51","lastverse":"51","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.51","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.51","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:51","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.050,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.052,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.51\" class=\"v\">51<\/sup>Puis il monta vers eux dans la barque, et le vent cessa. Ils furent en eux-m\u00eames tout stup\u00e9faits et remplis d\u2019\u00e9tonnement;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.52","name":"Marc 6:52","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.52"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.50","name":"Marc 6:50","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.50"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"52","lastverse":"52","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.52","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.52","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:52","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.051,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.053,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.52\" class=\"v\">52<\/sup>car ils n\u2019avaient pas compris le miracle des pains, parce que leur c\u0153ur \u00e9tait endurci.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.53","name":"Marc 6:53","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.53"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.51","name":"Marc 6:51","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.51"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"53","lastverse":"53","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.53","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.53","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:53","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.052,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.054,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Gu\u00e9risons \u00e0 G\u00e9n\u00e9sareth<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 53-56: cf. Mt 14:34-36. Jn 6:22, etc.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.53\" class=\"v\">53<\/sup>\n    Apr\u00e8s avoir travers\u00e9 la mer, ils vinrent dans le pays de G\u00e9n\u00e9sareth, et ils abord\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.54","name":"Marc 6:54","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.54"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.52","name":"Marc 6:52","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.52"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"54","lastverse":"54","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.54","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.54","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:54","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.053,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.055,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.54\" class=\"v\">54<\/sup>Quand ils furent sortis de la barque, les gens, ayant aussit\u00f4t reconnu J\u00e9sus,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.55","name":"Marc 6:55","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.55"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.53","name":"Marc 6:53","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.53"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"55","lastverse":"55","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.55","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.55","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:55","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.054,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.006.056,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.55\" class=\"v\">55<\/sup>parcoururent tous les environs, et l\u2019on se mit \u00e0 apporter les malades sur des lits, partout o\u00f9 l\u2019on apprenait qu\u2019il \u00e9tait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.56","name":"Marc 6:56","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.56"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.54","name":"Marc 6:54","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.54"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"56","lastverse":"56","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.56","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.56","label":"","reference":"Marc 6:56","prev_osis_id":"Mark.006.055,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Mark.007.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Mark.6.56\" class=\"v\">56<\/sup>En quelque lieu qu\u2019il arriv\u00e2t, dans les villages, dans les villes ou dans les campagnes, on mettait les malades sur les places publiques, et on le priait de leur permettre seulement de toucher le bord de son v\u00eatement. Et tous ceux qui le touchaient \u00e9taient gu\u00e9ris.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Mark.6","name":"Marc 6","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.7.1","name":"Marc 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.7.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Mark.6.55","name":"Marc 6:55","id":"fra-LSG:Mark.6.55"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc579f053.02994879');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc579f053.02994879\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\